.fi
Nokizaru is an all-in-one web recon CLI intended for bug bounty/web app pentesting engagements.
It can collect common recon signals from a target such as HTTP headers, SSL/TLS certificate details, WHOIS, DNS records, subdomains,
crawler link extraction, directory enumeration, Wayback URLs, and also features a fast port scan.
.SH REQUIRED OPTIONS
.TS
box, allbox;
l l.
OPTION	MEANING
--url URL	Target URL (e.g. https://example.com)
.TE
.SH MODULE SELECTION OPTIONS
These options enable modules. You may enable multiple in one run.
.TS
box, allbox;
l l.
OPTION	MODULE
--headers	Header Information
--sslinfo	SSL Certificate Information
--whois	Whois Lookup
--crawl	Crawl Target
--dns	DNS Enumeration
--sub	Sub-Domain Enumeration
--dir	Directory Search
--wayback	Wayback URLs
--ps	Fast Port Scan
--full	Full Recon
--no-[MODULE]	Skip specified modules above during full scan (e.g. --no-dir)
--export	Write results to export directory
--project [NAME]	Enable a persistent workspace (profiles, caching, diffing)
--cache	Enable caching even without a project
--no-cache	Disable caching (even in a project)
--diff last / [ID]	Diff this run against the last (or another run ID in the workspace)
.TE
.SH EXTRA OPTIONS
.TS
box, allbox;
l l l.
OPTION	MEANING	DEFAULT / NOTES
-h, --help	Show help and exit	-
-nb	Hide Banner	-
-dt DT	Directory enum threads	50
-pt PT	Port scan threads	50
-T T	Request timeout (seconds)	30.0
-w W	Path to wordlist	wordlists/dirb_common.txt
-r	Allow Redirect	False
-s	Toggle SSL Verification	True
-sp SP	Specify SSL port	443
-d D	Custom DNS servers	1.1.1.1
-e E	File extension(s) (comma separated)	txt,xml,php,etc.
-o O	Export Format(s) (comma-separated)	txt,json,html
-cd CD	Change export base directory	~/.local/share/nokizaru
-of OF	Change export folder name	nk_<host>_<DD-MM-YYYY_HH:MM:SS>
-k K	Add API key (NAME@KEY)	shodan@key
.TE
.SH API KEYS
Some subdomain sources require API keys.
Keys may be provided via environment variables (NK_*) or saved to:
.IR ~/.config/nokizaru/keys.json .
.PP
.TS
box, allbox;
l l.
ENV VAR	PROVIDER
NK_BEVIGIL_KEY	BeVigil
NK_BINEDGE_KEY	BinaryEdge
NK_FB_KEY	Facebook
NK_HUNTER_KEY	Hunter
NK_NETLAS_KEY	Netlas
NK_SHODAN_KEY	Shodan
NK_VT_KEY	VirusTotal
NK_ZOOMEYE_KEY	ZoomEye
.TE
.PP
To add a key from the CLI:
.PP
.nf
nokizaru -k shodan@YOURKEY
.fi
.SH FILES
.TS
box, allbox;
